Package use_cases.generate_summary_use_case

Interface GenerateSummaryIB

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GenerateSummaryUCI
    public interface GenerateSummaryIB
    An interface that the GenerateSummaryUCI interactor implements to maintain the dependency inversion principle. It contains the method used to generate a new graphical summary.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      GenerateSummaryOD generateNewSummary​(GenerateSummaryID inputData)
      Generates the information needed for the graphical representation of the MonthlyStorage data associated with monthID in the currentSession.

    • Method Detail

      • generateNewSummary

        GenerateSummaryOD generateNewSummary​(GenerateSummaryID inputData)
                              throws EntityException
        Generates the information needed for the graphical representation of the MonthlyStorage data associated with monthID in the currentSession.
        Parameters:
        inputData - a GenerateSummaryID object holding the SessionStorage and monthID needed to retrieve data
        Returns:
        a GenerateSummaryOD object holding the information needed to plot the graphs.
        Throws:
        EntityException - if there is no MonthID corresponding to a month in a monthly storage. This error being raised is a sign that there is something broken in the way that the MonthlyStorage objects are stored in the SessionStorage, and is not something the user can fix.
